<!-- 
    This file is an EXAMPLE configuration file.  While the configuration presented in this 
    example file is functional, it isn't very interesting.  It is here only as a start point
    for your deployment process.
    
    Very few attribute definitions and data connectors are demonstrated.

    Attribute-resolver-full.xml contains many examples of attributes, encoders, and a data
    connectors. Deployers should refer to the Shibboleth documentation for a complete list
    of components and their options.
